# gRPC Proto Files Directory

This directory contains all `.proto` files for gRPC contracts.

## Structure

- `users.proto` - User service gRPC contract
- `stories.proto` - Story service gRPC contract
- `search.proto` - Search service gRPC contract
- `comments.proto` - Comment service gRPC contract
- `ai.proto` - AI service gRPC contract
- `notification.proto` - Notification service gRPC contract

## Usage

Use `ts-proto` to auto-compile `.proto` files to TypeScript code.

